on-squaresmall-close{background-position:-80px -208px}.ui-icon-grip-dotted-vertical{background-position:0 -224px}.ui-icon-grip-dotted-horizontal{background-position:-16px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-solid-vertical{background-position:-32px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-solid-horizontal{background-position:-48px -224px}.ui-icon-gripsmall-diagonal-se{background-position:-64px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-diagonal-se{background-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta lo s\u1ee3 Real Madrid s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Champions League, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. Khi Real \u0111\u1ee5ng PSG \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh phong \u0111\u1ed9 sa s\u00fat, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1ecd. V\u00e0 ngay t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu, khi Adrien Rabiot m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat 33, nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u Los Blancos c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u00ec sao? \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League, Real ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i PSG 3-1. T\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, B\u1ea7y k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y 2-1. Chung cu\u1ed9c, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Zinedine Zidane gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern vs Real ban ket C1 Hum buon, Ken ken cung chang vui gi hinh anh\" title=\"Bayern vs Real b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1 H\u00f9m bu\u1ed3n, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng vui g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Bayern-vs-Real-ban-ket-C1-Hum-buon,-Ken-ken-cung-chang-vui-gi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real Madrid t\u1eebng l\u00e2m v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc hi\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i v\u00e0 m\u00e1u c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed9t c\u00f9ng. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 xem l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Real t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Juventus t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League 1 ng\u00e0y, Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua c\u00fa s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia kh\u00e1c. H\u1ecd d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc AS Roma t\u1edbi 4-1 sau tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i nh\u01b0ng thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 3-0 l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn d\u1eebng cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ban thang cua Ronaldo dua Real vao ban ket Champions League\" title=\"B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0a Real v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/hau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-khi-ranh-gioi-ong-lon-da-nhat-nhoa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng Los Blancos \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ngh\u0129 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 d\u00e0nh cho Real song \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. C\u0169ng b\u1ecb thua 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n s\u1edbm h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zidane r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 Marcelo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Real vs Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e2m v\u00e0o ngh\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i k\u1ecbp l\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3 penalty b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd gi\u00fap Real l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1ea3 s\u1eed n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, m\u1ed9t Real \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3 Juventus. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi gi\u1eefa t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kh\u00ed ch\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-madrid-13-juventus-nga-mu-truoc-nhung-chien-binh-cua-allegri-184-184090.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/du-am-real-madrid-13-juventus-nga-mu-truoc-nhung-chien-binh-cua-allegri.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-madrid-13-juventus-nga-mu-truoc-nhung-chien-binh-cua-allegri-184-184090.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Real Madrid 1-3 Juventus: Ng\u1ea3 m\u0169 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh c\u1ee7a Allegri</span><br>\r\n<span>Ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i \u2013 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac chung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c Juvetini tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh, nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nBayern l\u00e3o luy\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Jupp Heynckes \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u201cthay da, \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1ecbt\u201d Bayern Munich. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Carlo Ancelotti, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Bavaria r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n t\u1eeb trong ra ngo\u00e0i. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, h\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng cho t\u1edbi khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc PSG c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Bayern tr\u1edf n\u00ean ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0110\u1ee9c phanh phui s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 5 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Allianz Arena c\u00f4ng khai ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i Ancelotti. V\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich ban ket Champions League\" title=\"Bayern Munich b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/c1bayern.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bayern ti\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, Heynckes tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n \u1edf Bayern v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c thay \u0111\u1ed5i theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. \u0110\u1ebfn gi\u1edd n\u00e0y, \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Bundesliga l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Ancelotti l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c uy t\u00edn t\u1ea1i Bayern nh\u01b0 Heynckes. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 72 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 4 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Bavaria, t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng g\u1ea7n 8 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u00d4ng hi\u1ec3u r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1eeb h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/bayern-da-tim-duoc-hlv-thay-jupp-heynckes-184-184145.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2013/10/jupp-heynckes-vui-mung-sau-khi-tro-thanh-hlv-xuat-sac-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/bayern-da-tim-duoc-hlv-thay-jupp-heynckes-184-184145.html\">Bayern \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV thay Jupp Heynckes</span><br>\r\n<span>Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0110\u1ee9c, t\u00e2n HLV Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u2013 sau khi Jupp Heynckes gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p nhau</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Heynckes, Bayern Munich \u0111ang m\u01a1 t\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0103n 3 tuy\u1ec7t h\u1ea3o, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1eebng x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0o m\u00f9a 2012/13 d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n l\u00e3o luy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u Bayern vs Real b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean xem ra \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n. So v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Liverpool hay AS Roma, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat. V\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0o c\u00e1c \u0111\u00eam 24/4 v\u00e0 1/5 t\u1edbi, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich vs Real Madrid\" title=\"Bayern Munich vs Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Ket-qua-Boc-tham-ban-ket-Champions-League-201718-Bayern-dai-chien-Real-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bayern vs Real b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1 m\u00f9a 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd: Real \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng Bayern trong c\u1ea3 5 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, bao g\u1ed3m 3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 2 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh. Ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, ngay m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ai ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Real th\u1eafng Bayern 2-1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c. Nh\u01b0ng khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Santiago Bernabeu, \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d v\u1eabn l\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5. Sau \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 b\u1edfi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong th\u1eddi gian th\u00eam gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a Real song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1edfi 2 trong \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb b\u1ecb c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1ecf qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-danh-4-clb-vao-ban-ket-champions-league-ong-vua-va-thang-lieu-184-184158.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/diem-danh-4-clb-vao-ban-ket-champions-league-ong-vua-va-thang-lieu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-danh-4-clb-vao-ban-ket-champions-league-ong-vua-va-thang-lieu-184-184158.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m danh 4 CLB v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League: \u00d4ng Vua v\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng li\u1ec1u</span><br>\r\n<span>Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay (13/4), h\u00e3y \u0111i\u1ec3m qua s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 sau g\u1ea7n 1 n\u0103m, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Bayern th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh Niklas Sule, James Rodriguez, Sebastian Rudy, Corentin Tolisso hay Sandro Wagner \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng b\u1ed5 xung c\u1ee7a Real nh\u01b0 Jesus Vallejo, Theo Hernandez, Dani Ceballos \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, Bayern vs Real b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1 l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c. Th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f4i khi s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a 2012/13, HLV Heynckes x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern (Nico Kovac thay th\u1ebf). Li\u1ec7u l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00f3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 khi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u c\u00f9ng \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u hay kh\u00f4ng, ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-boc-tham-ban-ket-champions-league-201718-18h00-ngay-134-372-184166.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/160536-truc-tiep-boc-tham-ban-ket-champions-league-201718-18h00-ngay-134.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-boc-tham-ban-ket-champions-league-201718-18h00-ngay-134-372-184166.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ed1c th\u0103m b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18: Bayern \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Real</span><br>\r\n<span>T\u1ea1i l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia c\u1eb7p b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf Nyon, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 l\u00fac 18h15, l\u00e1 th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i \