n'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Man City run s\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc MU. </strong>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 34 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0o tay Man United. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Man City s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i Wembley (g\u1eb7p Tottenham), v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd n\u1ebfm m\u00f9i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin bong da 24h sang 144 Man City run so truoc MU hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng 144 Man City run s\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/bi-loai-xung-dang-khoi-c1-pep-van-trut-gian-len-trong-tai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng Man City s\u1ebd tu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Kane \u0111ang h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u00ec &ldquo;h\u00f4i&rdquo; b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. </strong>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i Tottenham y\u00eau c\u1ea7u BTC &ldquo;tr\u1ea3&rdquo; l\u1ea1i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho m\u00ecnh. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, v\u00e0 theo HLV Pochettino, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>MU ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ho\u00e3n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eeda Old Trafford. </strong>V\u1edbi \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i th\u00eam v\u00e0i ngh\u00ecn ch\u1ed7, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng m\u1ecdi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i Nh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1, v\u00e0 m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t SV\u0110 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng BL\u0110 Man United s\u1ebd t\u1ea1m ho\u00e3n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u01b0\u1ee3n Etihad c\u1ee7a g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m \u1ed3n \u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Conte th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf bay kh\u1ecfi Top 4. </strong>Trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong Top 4. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Conte mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Chelsea. Hi\u1ec7n nay, h\u1ecd \u0111ang k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Tottenham 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 6 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa (t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f9).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Salah \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League.</strong> M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng 3, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Cris Ronaldo hay Thierry Henry trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. N\u0103m nay, &ldquo;Th\u00e1nh Salah&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 \u0111o\u1ea1t gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11, th\u00e1ng 2 v\u00e0 th\u00e1ng 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin bong da 7/4: Salah nhan giai thuong cau thu xuat sac nhat thang 3\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 7/4: Salah nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/sal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 7/4: Salah nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng 3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>UEFA l\u1ea1i t\u1eb7ng qu\u00e0 Real Madrid. </strong>C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, trung v\u1ec7 Sergio Ramos s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t b\u1ed5 sung, sau h\u00e0nh vi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Bernabeu v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ec3 tranh c\u00e3i v\u1edbi HLV Max Allegri (Ramos b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2). \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng v\u1edbi K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng, v\u00ec h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi bayern Munich \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1151","checkdouble":"184189"},{"date":"06:39 14/04","title":"G\u1eb7p Real, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Bayern m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/16/gap-real-thuyen-truong-bayern-mo-ve-chuc-vo-dich-champions-league.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-we