1ee7a Bayern Munich</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jupp Heynckes, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u (m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa) v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p. CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League n\u0103m nay, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Bundesliga l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Bayern v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 (g\u1eb7p Real Madrid) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00e1 th\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Jupp Heynckes th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn. &ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft li\u1ec7u AS Roma hay Liverpool c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jupp Heynckes mu\u1ed1n Bayern v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Cup C1\" title=\"HLV Heynckes mu\u1ed1n Bayern v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Cup C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/16/so-thua-nhu-mu-bayern-khong-dam-xem-thuong-sevilla.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jupp Heynckes mu\u1ed1n Bayern v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Cup C1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>H\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Bayern c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Leo Messi, Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Maradona, ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i Messi, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn. H\u00e3y hy v\u1ecdng Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y t\u1ed1t l\u00e0nh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Los Blancos c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ngai v\u00e0ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa hattrick l\u00ean ng\u00f4i t\u1ea1i Champions League. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n Bayern Munich v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Cup C1 trong l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft, HLV Jupp Heynckes c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/bayern-vs-real-ban-ket-champions-league-hum-buon-ken-ken-cung-chang-vui-gi-184-184184.html\">Bayern vs Real b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League: H\u00f9m bu\u1ed3n, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng vui g\u00ec</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/bayern-da-tim-duoc-hlv-thay-jupp-heynckes-184-184145.html\">Bayern \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV thay Jupp Heynckes</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-mua-tien-dao-karim-benzema-197-184153.html\">Benzema c\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1ng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/trong-tai-tang-pen-cho-real-duoc-ca-ngoi-hay-nhat-nuoc-anh-184-184170.html\">Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i t\u1eb7ng pen cho Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i hay nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1150","checkdouble":"184191"},{"date":"23:21 13/04","title":"MU l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Herrera","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/28/mu-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-voi-herrera.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weigh