orner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Herrera kh\u00f3 tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Herrera \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Man United t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Tuy v\u1eady, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea5p b\u00eanh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-cong-bo-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-nam-khong-phai-ibrahimovic-172-160221.html\" target=\"_blank\">Herrera \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man United \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17</span>. Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Jose Mourinho. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Matic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Herrera. <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU tinh gia han hop dong voi Herrera hinh anh\" title=\"MU t\u00ednh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Herrera h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/28/mu-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-voi-herrera.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU t\u00ednh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Herrera</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng Man United v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef anh l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. V\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n anh qua n\u0103m 2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Herrera \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: <em>\u201cCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United t\u1edbi h\u1ebft th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hay kh\u00f4ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng hai b\u00ean ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cD\u0129 nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i s\u1ebd vui h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. M\u1ed7i khi v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui v\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-khong-ban-rashford-voi-bat-cu-gia-nao-172-184092.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/11/chuyen-nhuong-mu-khong-ban-rashford-voi-bat-cu-gia-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-khong-ban-rashford-voi-bat-cu-gia-nao-172-184092.html\">Man United ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sao tr\u1ebb Rashford</span><br>\r\n<span>L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Manchester United m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Marcus Rashford. Theo \u0111\u00f3, MU kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Rashford d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Herrera kh\u00f4ng th\u00f9 h\u1eb1n Matic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Matic khi\u1ebfn Herrera m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh kh\u00f4ng phi\u1ec1n l\u00f2ng v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Matic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Busquets. V\u00e0 Matic c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra cho HLV nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMourinho lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 b\u1ea1n n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u hay kh\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i \u00edch t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Man United:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/inter-milan-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-sao-bu-real-176-184172.html\">Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U v\u1ee5 sao b\u1ef1 Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-tin-buon-vu-sao-fulham-172-184148.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 sao Fulham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rio-ferdinand-muon-mu-chieu-mo-sao-real-madrid-172-184095.html\">Rio Ferdinand mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-khong-ban-rashford-voi-bat-cu-gia-nao-172-184092.html\">Man United ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sao tr\u1ebb Rashford</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-arsenal-khuyen-bo-doi-sao-tre-som-roi-mu-172-184058.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Arsenal khuy\u00ean b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb s\u1edbm r\u1eddi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span 