n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Ph\u00e1p tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/bao-phap-he-lo-ngoi-sao-se-roi-mu-trong-he-toi-172-183971.html\" target=\"_blank\">Martial \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Old Trafford</span>. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1edfi anh t\u1ecf ra b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho cho ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. C\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Rashford \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t l\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alexis Sanchez c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t cho t\u1edbi khi Sanchez c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Rashford \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho len tieng canh bao Martial va Rashford hinh anh\" title=\"Mourinho l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial v\u00e0 Rashford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/mourinho-khuyen-rashford-va-martial-lam-quen-voi-ghe-du-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial v\u00e0 Rashford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Martial l\u1eabn Rashford. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n non kinh nghi\u1ec7m. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra s\u00e2n cho c\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cB\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh kinh t\u1ebf th\u00ec s\u1ebd th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. C\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, treo gi\u00f2, c\u1ea1n ki\u1ec7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c hay b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0o. S\u1ebd th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede m\u1ecdi CLB v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec h\u01a1n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-2-muc-tieu-thay-anthony-martial-172-184046.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/mu-chot-2-muc-tieu-thay-anthony-martial.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-2-muc-tieu-thay-anthony-martial-172-184046.html\">MU ch\u1ed1t 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay Anthony Martial?</span><br>\r\n<span>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Anthony Martial, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho t\u00f4i th\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c HLV kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa. V\u00ec m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e2m v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u1ea3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nRashford \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf 97 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 112 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi HLV Jose Mourinho l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n. Tuy v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111ang lo l\u1eafng cho su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Man United ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Brom tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Bournemouth. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Mourinho cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u1eddi gian ra s\u00e2n c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/inter-milan-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-sao-bu-real-176-184172.html\">Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U v\u1ee5 sao b\u1ef1 Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-tin-buon-vu-sao-fulham-172-184148.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 sao Fulham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rio-ferdinand-muon-mu-chieu-mo-sao-real-madrid-172-184095.html\">Rio Ferdinand mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-khong-ban-rashford-voi-bat-cu-gia-nao-172-184092.html\">Man United ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sao tr\u1ebb Rashford</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-25-trieu-bang-mua-hau-ve-southampton-172-184042.html\">M.U chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Southampton</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-2-muc-tieu-thay-anthony-martial-172-184046.html\">MU ch\u1ed1t 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay Anthony Martial?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1148","checkdouble":"184188"},{"date":"06:08 14/04","title":"Bay kh\u1ecfi Top 4, Conte \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/7/bay-khoi-top-4-conte-do-loi-cho-hoc-tro.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-siz