ius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn &ldquo;chung k\u1ebft Top 4&rdquo; v\u1edbi Tottenham ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 Champions League c\u1ee7a The Blues, v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd h\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp West Ham v\u00e0 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Southampton.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, HLV Antonio Conte chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong Top 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu l\u1ed7i nh\u01b0 nhau. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tham d\u1ef1 Champions League, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Champions League.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;H\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1ea1, b\u1edfi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1eddi CLB th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, m\u00e0 BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea loai khoi Top 4, Conte do loi cho hoc tro hinh anh\" title=\"Chelsea lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Top 4, Conte \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/Chelsea-loai-khoi-Top-4,-Conte-do-loi-cho-hoc-tro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Chelsea lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Top 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n r\u1ec7u r\u00e3 c\u00f9ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng, nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Antonio Conte \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1eafp t\u1edbi, The Blues v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn FA Cup \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng, c\u00f9ng 6 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ra ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft FA Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9, tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i trong s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; Conte k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn sau khi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn Chelsea lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Top 4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean bongda24h</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/morata-bao-chua-cho-mua-giai-te-hai-o-chelsea-172-184151.html\">Morata b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-tien-courtois-bo-chelsea-toi-psg-172-184149.html\">V\u00ec ti\u1ec1n, Courtois b\u1ecf Chelsea t\u1edbi PSG?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-khuyen-chelsea-ban-cau-thu-thay-vi-sa-thai-conte-172-184147.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i khuy\u00ean Chelsea gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Conte v\u00e0 b\u00e1n 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"artic