u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League</span>, HLV Mihail \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd xin t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lanh dao CLB FLC Thanh Hoa noi gi sau loi to cao cua HLV Mihail hinh anh\" title=\"L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau l\u1eddi t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o c\u1ee7a HLV Mihail h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/sau-marian-mihail-ai-se-tro-thanh-hlv-moi-cua-flc-thanh-hoa.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Mihail t\u1ed1 b\u1ecb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a 't\u1ea1o ph\u1ea3n'</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 'l\u1eadt gh\u1ebf'. Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u00f4ng Mihail \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i: \"T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y t\u00f4i kh\u1ecfi FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. H\u1ecd \u0111i qua nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Bakel l\u00e0 ch\u00e0o t\u00f4i, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0m ng\u01a1\".</p>\r\n<h2>Ph\u00eda FLC Thanh H\u00f3a n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u1ed3n \u00e0o xung quanh vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Thanh H\u00f3a 'l\u00e0m ph\u1ea3n', m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 HLV Mihail \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e1o Zing.vn d\u1eabn l\u1eddi m\u1ed9t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/sau-marian-mihail-ai-se-tro-thanh-hlv-moi-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-291-183998.html\" target=\"_blank\">FLC Thanh H\u00f3a</span> cho bi\u1ebft: \u201c\u0110\u00e3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady r\u1ed3i, sao c\u00f2n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng \u1ea5y tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ed3i. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 anh em c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, th\u1ebf kia. T\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi theo ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00f4i co l\u1eddi qua ti\u1ebfng l\u1ea1i. Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chia tay l\u00e0 n\u00ean vui v\u1ebb. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ch\u00ednh l\u1ea1i \u0111i \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i, d\u1ef1ng n\u00ean nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eadt v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 theo suy di\u1ec5n th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ra g\u00ec c\u1ea3\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Mihail th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00ec tri\u1ebft l\u00fd v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a HLV Mihail kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Romanio c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd s\u1ee3 thua v\u00e0 l\u00fang t\u00fang trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-tro-hlv-mihail-to-cao-nguoc-nhau-sau-chuoi-tran-te-hai-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-168-184167.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/22/thay-tro-hlv-mihail-to-cao-nguoc-nhau-sau-chuoi-tran-te-hai-cua-flc-thanh-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-tro-hlv-mihail-to-cao-nguoc-nhau-sau-chuoi-tran-te-hai-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-168-184167.html\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mihail t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1ee3c nhau sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a</span><br />\r\nSau khi xin r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, HLV Mihail \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o b\u1ecb h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 l\u00e0m ph\u1ea3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Thanh H\u00f3a m\u1edbi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (TTVN)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1145","checkdouble":"184174"},{"date":"15:41 13/04","title":"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i t\u1eb7ng pen cho Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i hay nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/trong-tai-tang-pen-cho-real-duoc-ca-ngoi-hay-nhat-nuoc-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,H