50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110i\u1ec1n t\u00ean Welbeck v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Henrikh Mkhitaryan d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1edbi CSKA Moscow h\u1ed3i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang tr\u00e1i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh cu\u1ed9c tranh gi\u00e0nh gi\u1eefa Danny Welbeck v\u00e0 Alex Iwobi. C\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southampton cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0 HLV Wenger l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n VEB Arena.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Danny Welbeck. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n trong 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Welbeck \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng thanh tho\u00e1t v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cao sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng nguy hi\u1ec3m khi b\u1ecb CSKA Moscow d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/du-am-cska-moscow-22-arsenal-lai-la-anh-danny-welbeck-172-184171.html\" target=\"_blank\">Welbeck \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Arsenal tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc CSKA&nbsp;Moscow</span> v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p tung l\u01b0\u1edbi CSKA \u1edf ph\u00fat 75 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung yeu to giup Arsenal thoat hiem truoc CSKA Moscow hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap Arsenal tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc CSKA Moscow h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/du-am-cska-moscow-22-arsenal-lai-la-anh-danny-welbeck.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Welbeck gi\u00fap Arsenal tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc CSKA&nbsp;Moscow</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>R\u00fat Jack Wilshere kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian h\u1ed3i sinh \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Wilshere b\u1ed7ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u sa s\u00fat b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Wilshere t\u1ea1i Moscow th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c. Anh chuy\u1ec1n h\u1ecfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 r\u00ea b\u00f3ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c. V\u1ec1 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Wilshere c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat kh\u00e1ng c\u1ef1. Sau khi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn 3 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Arsenal b\u1ecb r\u00fat ng\u1eafn xu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1, HLV Wenger \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay Wilshere b\u1eb1ng Calum Chambers. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb 23 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat v\u00e0 phong t\u1ecfa \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba. \u0110\u1ed9t nhi\u00ean, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf n\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi CSKA Moscow ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 v\u00ec \u00e1p l\u1ef1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi Arsenal, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 v\u00ec \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 quen thu\u1ed9c. H\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat l\u00e0 Arsenal s\u1ebd v\u1ee1 v\u1ee5n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin r\u1eb1ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m NHM c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Chambers t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00eam ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p cho tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal. Mohamed Elneny c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o lui v\u1ec1 s\u00e2u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Wenger \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Welbeck c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League n\u0103m nay.</em><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hoa-hu-via-cska-moscow-hlv-arsene-wenger-thua-nhan-arsenal-qua-chu-quan-184-184127.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hoa-hu-via-cska-moscow-hlv-arsene-wenger-thua-nhan-arsenal-qua-chu-quan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hoa-hu-via-cska-moscow-hlv-arsene-wenger-thua-nhan-arsenal-qua-chu-quan-184-184127.html\">H\u00f2a h\u00fa v\u00eda CSKA Moscow, HLV Arsene Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Arsenal qu\u00e1 ch\u1ee7 quan</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Arsene Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 l\u01a1i l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal su\u00fdt ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Europa League khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Ramsey\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ramsey\" title=\"Ramsey\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Ramsey-nen-dau-thi-dau,-giup-Arsenal-hu-via-vao-ban-ket-C2-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ramsey v\u1eabn ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ng ngay \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ramsey-chan-thuong-sau-tran-gap-cska-moscow-184-184142.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ramsey \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</span> sau pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n VEB Arena ngay sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft r\u00e1ch s\u00e2u \u1edf b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Ramsey v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 v\u00e1 t\u1ea1m v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t cho \u0111\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Anh t\u1ea1o ra 1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, 2 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng r\u00ea b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t. \u1ede m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Ramsey c\u0169ng c\u00f3 3 pha c\u1eaft b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>N\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Ramsey qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i. Anh gi\u00fap cho HLV Wenger ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 quy\u1ec1n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 xoay chuy\u1ec3n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam l\u1eeda cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u CSKA&nbsp;Moscow vs Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-cska-moscow-22-arsenal-lai-la-anh-danny-welbeck-172-184171.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m CSKA Moscow 2-2 Arsenal: L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 anh, Danny Welbeck</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/cska-22-arsenal-khi-arsene-wenger-nghi-qua-nhieu-184-184150.html\">CSKA 2-2 Arsenal: Khi Arsene Wenger ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/wenger-ngai-dung-do-atletico-o-ban-ket-europa-league-184-184144.html\">Wenger ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Atletico \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/vao-ban-ket-europa-league-mesut-ozil-thach-thuc-moi-doi-thu-184-184143.html\">V\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa Lea